# Workspace member crates land here as the design's build sequence progresses.
# Planned (per docs/prd.md + design doc):
#   claude_parser      — read ~/.claude/projects/**/*.jsonl, normalize to UsageEvent
#   window             — rolling 5-hour window utilization
#   predictor          — EWMA + warm-up state, predicted time-to-cap
#   openai_client      — OpenAI billing endpoints
#   state_coordinator  — actor that owns Snapshot + AppHandle (only writer of tray)
#   watcher            — notify + 1s debounce + 60s safety poll
#   keychain           — keyring wrapper for API keys
#   settings           — config serde + atomic save
